{"title":"Review: Pactimo’s winter cycling kit beats the cold, wind… and some rain","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/22/review-pactimos-winter-cycling-kit-beats-the-cold-wind-and-some-rain/","date":1614044406000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>I’ve been riding out the worst of our winter weather here in the damp, very cold central North Carolina with a stubborn refusal to join the ranks of trainer athletes indoors. Meaning many of my rides are slightly to extremely damp, quite cold, and sometimes windy.</p><p>Fortunately, the combination of Pactimo’s Vertex WX-D jacket with the Storm+ Thermal LS Jersey underneath worked great to keep my core warm (with a thin base layer, S/S or L/S depending on the day), and the Storm+ Thermal Bib Tights protected my stems.</p><h3>(BTW, they’re all on sale right now)</h3><p>It’s worth noting that, as we’re nearing Spring, all of these items are on sale. I list the MSRP below, but click the price link to get them for about half off. Just know that they’re blowing through popular sizes and colors, so hustle.</p><h2>Pactimo winter jersey &amp; jacket review</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11.jpg\" alt=\"pactimo winter cycling kit photos of thermal bibs and jacket with long sleeve jersey\" width=\"1300\" height=\"975\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1300px) 100vw, 1300px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11.jpg 1300w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-265x198.jpg 265w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11.jpg 1300w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-angles-11-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>The Vertex WX-D jacket is rated for 0º to 40º, so I should start with this: Pactimo is based in Colorado, where the air is dry and a sunny 40º day means residents are wearing shorts and a T-shirt.</p><p>Here on the east coast, it’s humid, and 40º is freakin’ cold. Like, this jacket is a good start, and then I add layers underneath, plus a neck gaiter. I also tested Pactimo’s waterproof&nbsp;<a href=\"https://alnk.to/hsofrA3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Alpine gloves</a>, and <a href=\"https://alnk.to/8Px7nCS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Alpine Thermal Cap</a>.</p><p>The cap wasn’t my favorite because the ear flaps didn’t stay down over my ears, which not only made them cold, but also created a tiny bit of wind noise. I like the visor for low winter sun, but I also felt like it trapped air against my forehead, making it freeze…and it didn’t really keep my ears warm, so I’ll stick to beanies.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05.jpg\" alt=\"pactimo winter riding kit and alpine waterproof road bike gloves\" width=\"1420\" height=\"525\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1420px) 100vw, 1420px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05.jpg 1420w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-800x296.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-768x284.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-696x257.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-1068x395.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-1136x420.jpg 1136w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05.jpg 1420w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-800x296.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-768x284.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-696x257.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-1068x395.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-05-1136x420.jpg 1136w\"></a></p><p>I <em>would</em> recommend the gloves for spring riding on their own, and cooler days with a set of thin liners. They’re surprisingly able to handle a liner without turning into “stuffed sausage” feeling fingers. Layered, they were enough for mid-40ºs, but not for this:</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12.jpg\" alt=\"riding bikes in the freezing rain\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-12-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>As happens, on the first day I was going to ride in the kit, I was racing incoming rain to get out the door. The rain won, and I set off in 34º rain. It was mainly just my hands that got too cold to take it, the kit did well enough considering. But I wouldn’t recommend riding in near-freezing rain for any reason.</p><figure id=\"attachment_251842\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-251842\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03.jpg\" alt=\"winter cycling jacket with two pockets\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-265x198.jpg 265w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-03-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-251842\">I fit my phone in one pocket, and a GoPro on a GorillaPod tripod and neck gaiter in the other…and barely noticed any of it was there.</figcaption></figure><p>The jacket has secondary cuffs that help it seal up around the gloves and prevent wind from sneaking in. For something this warm, it’s plenty soft, flexible, and reasonably lightweight, too.</p><p>It also has two main pockets plus a small zippered pocket for cash, keys, etc. The pockets are deep enough, but because there’s only two, they’re a bit wider than normal, so it’s not going to hold a phone as securely as a typical pocket.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-01.jpg\" alt=\"pactimo vertex winter cycling jacket review\" width=\"1420\" height=\"525\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1420px) 100vw, 1420px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-01.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-01.jpg 1420w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdn