0.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-details-07-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>The jacket gets a small zipper garage at the top, the jersey does not. And sure enough, I nicked my neck with the zipper. Despite that, they’re fairly comfortable with them zipped all the way up…which isn’t always the case for jackets and jerseys with a raised collar. I still think offset zippers are ideal for preventing it from poking into my adam’s apple, but these aren’t the worst. Actually, the jacket’s collar/zip comfort is fine; the jersey is OK.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08.jpg\" alt=\"pactimo brushed fleece winter cycling jersey with DWR treatment\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-265x198.jpg 265w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-reviewdetails-08-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>The Storm+ Thermal jersey gets a water-shedding DWR treatment…which I didn’t really get a chance to test under the jacket. I can say it’s warm, and comfortable, with a zoned construction that’s readily apparent when I held the jersey up to the light. Interestingly, the warmer fleeced front area lets more light through than the back and side panels, but it’s definitely a bit thicker.</p><p>It should be a great spring piece, too, without the outer layer hiding it. I love the striped graphics’&nbsp;eyecatching, multi-colored pattern that should stand out on the road.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-03.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-03.jpg\" alt=\"waterproof cycling jersey shown with rain soaking it\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-03.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-03.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pactimo-winter-riding-kit-review-after-rain-03-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/pa